{"id":98,"idInBook":4224,"chapterId":22,"bookId":14,"arabic":"وَعَنْ أَنَسٍ قَالَ: إِنَّ نَعْلَ النَّبِيِّ صَلَّى الله عَلَيْهِ وَسلم كَانَ لَهَا قبالان","english":{"narrator":"","text":"Anas said the Prophet’s sandal had two thongs. \nBukhari transmitted it."},"hadithNumber":4224,"hadithId":98,"reference":"22:98","meta":{"id":"mishkat_almasabih","length":4428,"totalChapters":25,"arabic":{"title":"مشكاة المصابيح","author":"الإمام الكاتب التبريزي"},"english":{"title":"Mishkat Al Masabih","author":"Al-Khatib Al-Tabrizi"}},"chapter":{"id":22,"bookId":14,"arabic":"كتاب اللباس","english":"Clothing","startHadith":4127,"endHadith":4319,"totalHadiths":193},"version":{"name":"mishkat_almasabih","title":"Mishkat Al Masabih","chapters":25}}